dojox.image
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 0.9
Release date: 08/29/07
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Project state:
prototype | expermental
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Credits
	Peter Higgins (phiggins@gmail.com)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Project description

	A class to provide a common API for images, and home for image
	related Widgets.
 
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Dependencies:

	LightBox: dojo core, dojox.fx and optionally dojox.data. uses
	either tundra or soria theme, no standalone icons.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Documentation

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Installation instructions

	there is no rollup for dojox.image, so you simply need the
	dojox/image folder and all of it's children to live in your
	dojox root.  
	
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Additional Notes

	LightBox: currently works as individual items, and grouped items,
	but usage of dojox.data.FlickrStore is broken because all images
	are grouped in one master group, the API is subject to change, and
	is marked accordingly.

	Hoping to implement: Picker, SlideShow, Carossel, Gallery using
	a common API provided by dojox.image.Pane (?) 